title: Ep 48 - Secrets to Getting Successful Mentors w/ Geoff Woods
itunes:title: Ep 48 - Secrets to Getting Successful Mentors w/ Geoff Woods
description:
We all know that we are the average of the five people that we spend the most time with. Geoff Woods runs The Mentee Podcast and has spent countless hours developing a system to surround himself with the most successful people that he can. In this episode he shares some of his secrets to networking, as well as secrets to get successful people to be your mentor.
